@clw22580  A- DLSS also have Super Sampling that does not create fake frames giving you basically no visual hit while giving you 2-3x the frame rate without creating fake frames

B- 1x Frame Gen is genuinely good, it works fantastically IMHO and the fake frames with Reflex introduce .003 sec of delay, less than a frame at 60fps, actually this delay only noticeable at 144hz, which is fair, but here is the thing, you have to be already running the game close to 100fps, if you are playing competitive, deactivate this and turn down graphics, if you are not playing competitive, the delay is nothing

3- RT is very easily noticeable, what the fuck you on about? I can tell immediately the difference between Raster and RT, and even with my 4060ti, whenever I have the chance I enable RT

